data.description: Very nice townhome in Sequoia Village.  This 1650 sqft towhnome was built in 2007, has 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, with a half bath downstairs.  Nice kitchen, large living area, and nice patio area. Property is currently tenant occupied, very cooperative, thus short notice often works.  Tenant will be moving out end of March.  Current rent is $1900/mo.  Tenant has 4 kids, hence their bedrooms are a bit cluttered.  Carpets will be professionally cleaned.    ***This is Not in Chambers Field it is clearly in the Ranchos, however the MLS insists on 315 zone***
